Author: zoonosis
Title: [BXUNTY] KlickZie Bounty Campaign! | By Tautachrome, Inc. | klickzie.io
Body: The KlickZie Bounty Campaign ...by Tautachrome, Inc. The Bounty Campaign will run from December 13th - February 6th!     To get in touch with the Bitcointalk BXUNTY Team, simply visit: www.t.me/BXUNTY        For this Bitcointalk Bounty Campaign, 200,000 KLK have been reserved to be distributed to participants. KlickZie Tokens are ERC20 Tokens which will be distributed among the participants in the bounty campaign based on stakes earned in each bounty component, given the allocations for each as seen below.  Bounty Components 1. Telegram Campaign - 5% 2. Facebook Campaign- 20% 3. Twitter Campaign - 20% 4. Article/Media Campaign - 25% 5. LinkedIn Campaign  10% 6. Translation Campaign - 5% 7. Referral Campaign - 10% 8. Signature Campaign - 5%   IMPORTANT: Once a participants registers with a ERC-20 ETH Address, do not change address throughout the campaign! Only provide ETH address to which you know the private keys or seed phrases. (No exchanges, Shapeshift, or other 3rd party services). Send us your public ERC20 Address  --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------  ATTENTION: High-Effort Tasks ONLY require proof of participation in order to prevent fraud & protect our bounty hunters.  PLEASE READ & FOLLOW: Bitcointalk Pinned Bounty Rules: https://bitcointalk.org/index.php?topic=3953664.0  IN ORDER TO PARTICIPATE IN THE WEEKLY TWITTER, WEEKLY LINKEDIN, , YOUTUBE, ARTICLE & SIGNATURE CAMPAIGNS, PLEASE FOLLOW ALL INSTRUCTIONS AND SUBMIT THE FOLLOWING APPLICATION IN THIS THREAD:  Code: #KLICKZIEProofOfParticipation Bitcointalk Username: Campaigns Joined:   *Absolutely no spamming. DO NOT POST IN THE THREAD if you are performing low effort tasks such as only following social media or Telegram AS THIS IS AGAINST BITCOINTALK RULES. ONLY post if you are performing high-effort tasks such as the ones listed above!*     -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- The bounty campaign is now over! --------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------    1. KlickZie Telegram Campaign - 5%  Rewards:  Telegram Channel Registration: 1 Stake  Guidelines:  To earn 1 Share, you need to Join our official Telegram channel.  You must remain in the Telegram channel until conclusion of the bounty campaign!  YOU MUST DIRECT MESSAGE THE FOLLOWING CODE TO @CRYPTOBOUNTYMANAGER ON TELEGRAM. DO NOT POST IN THE KLICKZIE CHANNEL OR YOU MAY BE DISQUALIFIED!  *SEND THIS IN A DIRECT MESSAGE TO @CRYPTOBOUNTYMANAGER ON TELEGRAM. DO NOT POST IN THE CHANNEL OR IN THIS THREAD!* Code: #JOINKLICKZIETELEGRAM  Bitcointalk Username: Telegram Username: @   How To Apply: Join our Telegram Group Telegram Registration Form  Check Telegram Spreadsheet: Here    2. KlickZie Facebook Campaign - 20%  Official KlickZie Facebook Group  Rewards:  2 Stakes / 1 Facebook Post about Klickzie  1 Stake / 1 Facebook Share of Klickzie account post  IN ORDER TO SUBMIT CLAIM FORMS, FILL IN YOUR WEEKLY REPORT FORMS HERE WEEKLY. You can submit as soon as you've reached 5 Posts & 5 Shares. Weekly Facebook Report Form (January 31st to February 6th)  Guidelines:  Follow and like the official Tautachrome Facebook page until after the end of the token sale  One facebook account per bitcoin talk member is allowed.  Your facebook account must have at least 500 friends.  All posts AND profiles will be reviewed by bounty campaign managers.  MAXIMUM 5 POSTS WEEKLY  MAXIMUM 5 FACEBOOK SHARES WEEKLY  Maximum 15 Stakes Earned WEEKLY  Posts and Profile must be public.  Submit weekly forms by latest the day the week is over in order to earn your shares.  How to Apply: Facebook Registration Form  Check Facebook Spreadsheet: Here    3. KlickZie Twitter Campaign - 20%  Official KlickZie Twitter  Rewards:  2 stakes / 1 Tweet about KlickZie  1 stakes / 1 Retweet of KlickZie account tweet  IN ORDER TO SUBMIT CLAIM FORMS, FILL IN YOUR WEEKLY REPORT FORMS HERE WEEKLY. You can submit as soon as you've reached 5 Tweets & 5 Retweets. Weekly Twitter Report Form (January 31st to February 6th)  Guidelines:  You must follow @Tautachrome_Inc until after the end of the token sale.  One twitter account per bitcoin talk member is allowed.  Your twitter account must have at least 300 authentic followers.  All tweets will be reviewed by bounty campaign managers.  Twitter Audit must be better than 80% (No Bot Behavior)  MAXIMUM 5 Retweets WEEKLY  MAXIMUM 5 Tweets WEEKLY  MAXIMUM 15 stakes WEEKLY  Submit weekly forms by latest the day the week is over in order to earn your stakes.  A Tweet must include at least one hashtag: #KlickZie $KLK  How to Apply: Twitter Registration Form  Check Twitter Spreadsheet: Here    4. KlickZie Articles/Media Campaign - 25%  Rewards:  All submitted Videos will receive 2 stakes.  All submitted Articles will receive 1 stake.  Guidelines:  A maximum of three articles and/or videos are eligible for stakes.  All articles or blog posts must be publicly viewable.  The platform through which you publish must be relevant and there must be an audience.  Pieces should be at least 400 words and include the links to our website (https://klickzie.io)  How to Apply: KlickZie Article/Media Registration Form  Check Article/Media Campaign Spreadsheet: Here    5. KlickZie LinkedIn Campaign - 10%  Official KlickZie LinkedIn  Rules:  In order to earn 1 Stake, you must follow KlickZie on LinkedIn: https://www.linkedin.com/company/KlickZie-one  You can earn 1 more stake per week by making a quality post about KlickZie on LinkedIn! You must submit the claim form the week you make the post.  Rewards:  1 Stake for following KlickZie on LinkedIn  1 Stake / 1 Post about KlickZie on LinkedIn WEEKLY  IN ORDER TO SUBMIT CLAIM FORMS, FILL IN YOUR REPORT FORMS HERE WEEKLY. You can submit as soon as you've made your post about KlickZie. Weekly LinkedIn Report Form (January 31st to February 6th)  How to Apply: LinkedIn Registration Form  Check LinkedIn Spreadsheet: Here    6. KlickZie Translation Campaign - 5%  Rewards:  Whitepaper Translation: 200 stakes  Whitepaper Updates: 20 stakes Each Update  Website Translation: 25 stakes  One Pager Translation: 25 stakes  Guidelines:  TRANSLATORS WHO APPLY FOR ALL WILL BE GIVEN PRIORITY  Absolutely no google translator is permitted to be used. Participants using google translator will not be accepted and if a google translation is submitted, that translator will be blacklisted!  Please do not submit a request to translate unless you are fluent in the translated language and in English.  Managers/Owners reserve the right to make minor, reasonable changes to the rules.  How to Apply: To reserve, please post:   Your Language:  Reference to previous works (at least 3):  Translating Whitepaper, ANN thread, One-Pager or all:  Once you are messaged, you will fill out the Translation Registration Form, and show up on the spreadsheet below.  Completed Translations:    7. KlickZie Referral Campaign - 10%  Rewards  1 Stake per referral signed up using your referral link  How to Apply  Sign up at https://wallet.klickzie.io/#/signup in order to receive your referral link.  Referral Registration Form  Guidelines  Sign up on the KlickZie website in order to receive your referral link.  Every user that signs up using your referral link will grant you one stake.  Check Referral Spreadsheet: Here    8. KlickZie Signature Campaign - 5%  Rewards: 1. Jr. Member: 15 stakes/Week 2. Member: 20 stakes/Week 3. Full Member: 30 stakes/Week 4. Sr. Member: 50 stakes/Week 5: Hero Member: 65 stakes/Week 6: Legendary Member: 80 stakes/Week  +5 stakes/Week for wearing our Avatar!  Guidelines:  Must make at least 5 constructive posts on Bitcoin Talk Forum per week.  No negative trust accounts please  The Bounty Manager will update spreadsheets every week and check that the signature is still being used week after week.
